en_376966_0	A musical show, organized by the Army made the people in and around Paranthan to enjoy the evening, keeping their tiring routine work aside for a moment.
en_376966_1	Musicians in 1 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment (SLSR) band entertained the crowd allowing some of the participants to exhibit their singing talents to the audience with the performing band.
en_376966_2	The event also helped build confidence among residents eliminating their fear psychosis after April 21 attacks.
en_376966_3	Brigadier Shantha Hewawitharana, Commander 57 Division and his subordinate Commanders in the 572 Brigade and 1 SLSR battalion organized the event on the directions given by the Commander Security Forces - Kilinochchi Major General Vijitha Ravipriya.
